@description:
"""
Sujet : Parsing de CV ou l'extraction de données à partir de CV
Concevoir et développer un outil d'extraction automatique des données pertinentes de différentes sources de CV (principalement PDF et Word), de les transformer pour que chaque ensemble de données soit conforme aux exigences de l'outil MySkills  et les charger dans un fichier Excel ou ils seront facilement accessibles pour analyse et export.
Objectifs :
    Identifier les solutions possibles pour extraire les données. Par exemple étudier les ETL du marché (Talend ou autre)
    Extraire et transformer les données selon le format suivant :
        Synthèse
            Titre
            Nombre d'année d'expérience
            Savoir-faire
            Savoir-être
        Compétences
            Langages
            Méthodes / architectures
            Framework / API / Webservices / CMS
            Stockage / Base de données / BI
            Devops / Cloud / IA
            Outils / Logiciels / ERP
        Formations
            Année / Diplôme / Université ou école
        Langues
            Français / Anglais
        Certifications
            Date / nom de la certification
        Expériences professionnelles
            Titre
            Poste / fonction
            Client
            Projet
            Tâches
            Outils / Méthodologie
    Chargement sous format Excel
Résultats attendus : gain du temps pour les chargés de recrutement
"""
[] Research and Analysis
    [] Study existing ETL tools (e.g., Talend) and their suitability for this project
    [] Investigate open-source libraries for PDF and Word document parsing
    [] Analyze AI-powered resume parsing solutions


[] Design Phase
    [] Create a high-level system architecture
    [] Design the data extraction and transformation pipeline
    [] Define the output Excel file structure


[] Development Environment Setup
    [] Set up the development environment with necessary tools and libraries
    [] Create a version control repository for the project


[] Data Extraction
    [] Develop modules to read PDF and Word documents
    [] Implement text extraction from these documents


[] Data Parsing and Transformation
    [] Create parsers for each section of the resume (Summary, Skills, Experience, etc.)
    [] Develop algorithms to identify and categorize different types of information
    [] Implement data cleaning and normalization procedures


[] Output Generation
    [] Develop a module to create and populate Excel files with extracted data
    [] Ensure the output format matches the MySkills tool requirements


[] Integration
    [] Combine all modules into a cohesive pipeline
    [] Implement error handling and logging


[] Testing
    [] Develop a comprehensive test suite
    [] Perform unit testing for each module
    [] Conduct integration testing of the entire pipeline
    [] Test with a diverse set of resume samples


[] Optimization
    [] Analyze performance and optimize for speed and accuracy
    [] Implement parallel processing if necessary


[] User Interface (Optional)
    [] Develop a simple user interface for file input and output management


[] Documentation
    [] Write technical documentation for the system
    [] Create user manuals for recruitment managers


[] Deployment
    [] Prepare the system for deployment in the target environment
    [] Set up any necessary infrastructure


[] Training
    [] Conduct training sessions for recruitment managers


[] Maintenance and Support
    [] Establish a system for ongoing maintenance and support
    [] Plan for future updates and improvements


[] Evaluation
    [] Measure time savings for recruitment managers
    [] Gather feedback and identify areas for improvement



